Package de.gmxhome.conrad.jpos.jpos_base.itemdispenser

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ItemDispenserInterface
    Interface for methods that implement property setter and method calls for the ItemDispenser device category.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Factory
    General part of ItemDispenser factory for JPOS devices using this framework.
    ItemDispenserProperties
    Class containing the item dispenser specific properties, their default values and default implementations of ItemDispenserInterface.
    ItemDispenserService
    ItemDispenser service implementation.
    ItemDispenserStatusUpdateEvent
    Status update event implementation for ItemDispenser devices.
